    "b, Detected N-photon coincidence rates for N-photon inputs as a function of time, with the photonic circuit configured to implement the identity matrix.",
    "The rates are integrated for 50 s. The grey areas correspond to maintenance and upgrade periods.",
    "In the right figure, we also monitor the on-chip photon indistinguishability and single-photon purity, as quantified by the Hong-Ou-Mandel (HOM) visibility V HOM and 1 - g (2) (0), respectively, where g (2) is the normalized second-order correlation function.",
    "HOM kT is V HOM for delays k × ΔT between emitted photons where ΔT = 180 ns.",
    "Each data point corresponds to a correlation histogram integrated over 10 s. c, Job execution flowchart on Ascella."
